---
source: tests/cli.rs
assertion_line: 35
expression: "help_output(& [\"use\", \"--help\"])"
---
Apply a template component to the current project

Usage: hpds use [OPTIONS] [COMPONENT]

Arguments:
  [COMPONENT]  Component to apply; omit to list the available components

Options:
      --kind <VALUE>         Component-specific variant (e.g. make, targets, or both for pipeline)
  -v, --verbose              Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)
      --force                Overwrite existing files that differ from the template
  -q, --quiet                Suppress all output except errors
      --language <LANGUAGE>  Project language; detected from project files (renv.lock, pyproject.toml, ...) when omitted [possible values: r, python, both]
      --no-color             Disable colored output
      --config <PATH>        Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml
      --workflows <NAMES>    gha workflows to add without prompting (comma-separated or repeated: pr-template, lint, audit-bot)
  -h, --help                 Print help
